  "text": "This is assessed with the 8-item Client Satisfaction Questionnaire-8, a briefer version of the larger Client Satisfaction Questionnaire [CITATION_1] . This measure is frequently used to assess participants' satisfaction with, and impression of the effectiveness of, the services they received. Items are rated on a four-point scale. This measure has good reliability (alpha coefficient = .93). It is administered at the post-treatment assessment only.",
